I '''Carlos Borromeo''' ({{lang-it|Carlo Borromeo}}, {{lang-la|Carolus Borromeus}}, 1538–1584) ing [[Cardinal (Catholicism)|cardinal]] [[Archdiocese of Milan|arsobispo ning Milano]] manibat 1564 anggang 1584. Metung ya i Borromeo kareng mapyang repormista ning magulung kalabing-anam a dilanwa o siglu, kayabe ya i San [[Ignacio de Loyola]], San [[Felipe Neri]], a menimuna king pangimut a labanan ing pamanyulung ning Protestaning Repormasyun. Manimuna yang tauan ning [[Counter-Reformation]], a yang penibatan da reng makabaldugang reporma o kapanumanan king [[Iglesia Catolica]], kayabe ya ing pamagtátag kareng [[seminaryu]] para king pamagaral da reng pari. Metung [[santu]] king [[Iglesia Catolica Church]], at keng 4 November ing kayang [[fiesta]].

